@token = eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOjEsInVzZXJuYW1lIjoiYWxpY2UiLCJpYXQiOjE3ODE2OTg3NDgsImV4cCI6MTc4MjMwMzU0OH0.jM_pdGWF4GkvSb1QPo3408ZDenGnhl66IIQ34rDO-Y8

### Get leaderboard (public, pas besoin de token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/scores

### Create score (auth requise)
POST {{baseUrl}}/scores
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "wave": 5,
  "points": 1250
}

### Create score sans token (doit échouer en 401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/scores
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wave": 3,
  "points": 800
}